    "orgId": "org-2",
    "projectId": "test",
    "branchId": "br-main-branch-123456"
  },
  "project": {
    "id": "test"
  },
  "message": "Linked <TMP>/agent_linked_existing/.neon to project test (org org-2) on branch br-main-branch-123456. Next: run \`neonctl env pull\` to write this branch’s env vars (DATABASE_URL, …) into a local .env"
}
"
`;

